data.description: Welcome to your dream single-story home in the highly sought-after Sun City Anthem Independence community! This meticulously maintained residence boasts 2 bedrooms, with the potential for a 3rd bedroom easily convertible (no closet currently). As you enter, the open floor plan welcomes you with a sense of spaciousness and versatility. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite countertops, upgraded cabinets, and a convenient work/desk area. The breakfast bar is perfect for casual dining, while the adjacent breakfast nook provides a cozy spot for morning meals. Step outside to discover a rare find – a large private yard surrounded by a block wall for added privacy. The outdoor space is complete with a built-in barbecue and a covered patio. This Sun City Anthem gem is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. The community offers loads of amenities; clubhouse, social calendar, community golf/pool/spa, exercise room, and more! Don't miss this opportunity!!
